    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make voter registration for general elections automatic",
        "additional_details": "This automatic voter registration would not create fraud issues, as many European countries that have automatic voter registration have proven. Automatic voter registration is a system that has been proved it works.",
        "background": "In countries with higher voter turnout, the governments make voter registration automatic and therefore much easier to vote. In a democracy it should be much easier to vote than it is right now. Automatic voter registration would make many more people actively involved in our democracy.",
